node.text:
SOOOOOooooo, I drew a li'l Twitchy for the Binding of Isaac: Four Souls Requiem alternate art cards set! AIN'T HE CUUUTE??? The cuuuutest! I love him. Adore him. Would die for him and never progress.

Haven't played the PC game in years but I fucked up the Mom's stiletto pretty bad once, so here's to you, past Amber. You did good.

[Go to TheFourSouls.com for more info.]
